---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Building Guides"
description: "Guides on pole barns, steel buildings, permits, and costs, written by the CNO Pole Barns crew that builds post-frame and erects Federal Steel buildings across Michigan."
permalink: /blog/
---

{# ========== BLOG INDEX ========== #}

<header class="ohero noimg slim">
  <div class="wrap"><div class="ohero-inner stagger">
    <span class="lab">Guides</span>
    <h1>Building Guides</h1>
    <p class="lead">Straight answers on pole barns, steel buildings, permits, and cost, written by the crew that pours the concrete and sets the trusses.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-gold">Get a Free Estimate</a>
    </div>
  </div></div>
</header>

<section class="blk"><div class="wrap">
  <div class="head reveal"><h2>All building guides</h2><p>Everything we've written about post-frame and steel buildings, permits, and planning a project in Michigan.</p></div>
  <div class="bloggrid stagger">
    {% for post in collections.blog %}
    <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="bcard">
      {% if post.data.image %}<div class="im"><img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" loading="lazy"></div>{% endif %}
      <div class="bd">
        <span class="meta">{{ post.data.category or "Guides" }} &middot; {{ post.data.date | dateFormat }}</span>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ post.templateContent | excerpt }}</p>
      </div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div></section>

<section class="blk cta"><div class="wrap"><div class="box reveal">
  <div>
    <h2>Have a project in mind?</h2>
    <p>Send us a few details and some photos of your site. We'll tell you straight whether post-frame or steel is the right call, and what it takes to get it built.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <a class="btn btn-gold" href="/contact/">Get a free estimate</a>
    <span class="or">or call</span>
    <a class="bigph" href="tel:{{ site.phoneTel }}">{{ site.phone }}</a>
  </div>
</div></div></section>
